reviewText: There is so little content here that it is pretty disappointing. The picture on the cover has nothing to do with anything, which is too bad because that looked like it was going to be helpful.
So little here I was dumbfounded, it's 14 minutes of an acting coach making the same obvious point regarding acting models, over and over.
The DVD has an amazing video index with topics that will take you to the exact place on the video where you want to go.  There are also easy to understand charts.
